==Description== <!--T:3-->

<!--T:4-->
The '''TechDraw ExtensionLockUnlockView''' tool locks or unlocks the position of a view by toggling its {{PropertyData|Lock Position}} property. A locked view has a fixed position relative to the page or the group it belongs to.

==Usage== <!--T:5-->

<!--T:6-->
# Select a single drawing view.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionLockUnlockView.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionLockUnlockView|Toggle View Lock]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|TechDraw → Attributes/Modifications → [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionLockUnlockView.svg|16px]] Toggle View Lock}} option from the menu.
# The {{PropertyData|Lock Position}} property of the view is toggled. Locked views have a red padlock icon [[Image:TechDraw_Lock.svg|16px]] in the lower left corner.


